g.title: j1338084053
g.text: So what made you want to keep rats as pets?

g.title: j1601873588
g.text: We're talking on the *internet* and you know the *phone* exists, yeah?

g.title: j2563127142
g.text: Sometimes painful memories are all that get us through.

g.title: j4236796905
g.text: I don't think I like where this is going. [End.]

g.title: j1592652735
g.text: Bien podría ser un pinche fantasma
Call from beyond the grave, can't change, can't live, can't die

g.title: j4213853406
g.text: What do you know of pain?

g.title: j1611640073
g.text: I want to know why you think I like rats

g.title: j2889416148
g.text: Like shadows on a VHS tape used one too many times

g.title: j4013718468
g.text: Do you know what it feels like to get your head cut off? I do. I've died a thousand times. And it *hurts,* lady.

g.title: j3003573750
g.text: I don't have to prove myself to you, lady.

g.title: j2008321640
g.text: No, better they think I am already dead
I take this pain for them

g.title: j1802296732
g.text: I did not ask you to

g.title: j2252332397
g.text: Because they're intelligent, affectionate, and playful?

g.title: j1331915387
g.text: Because they're often neglected and misunderstood?

g.title: j2309111689
g.text: Lettie? I don't understand the first thing about you. But the rats are cute as hell.

g.title: j192605700
g.text: There's still life worth living, here.

g.title: j2493011888
g.text: Do you take the pain for other people by choice, or because it's your duty?

g.title: j1600437771
g.text: Another fantasma like the rest of us
Reliving their deaths again and again and again

g.title: j3080350984
g.text: With Amir's games and Arthur's drinking and Aoi's music and Quincy's pictures

g.title: j160998517
g.text: Better they think I am already dead

g.title: j2324001914
g.text: I chose a long time ago
Now it's too late to go back

g.title: j1760239323
g.text: Didn't grow up with a lot of money as a kid
Rats were easy to keep, mi mamá didn't mind

g.title: j61553849
g.text: I have to get back to work
